        </li>
        <li class="about-vision-item">
          <span class="about-vision-numeral">II</span>
          <h3 class="about-vision-label"><em>Churches</em></h3>
          <p class="about-vision-body">Formed in scripture, sacrament, and conviction.</p>
        </li>
        <li class="about-vision-item">
          <span class="about-vision-numeral">III</span>
          <h3 class="about-vision-label"><em>Communities</em></h3>
          <p class="about-vision-body">Formed in membership, solidarity, and tradition.</p>
        </li>
        <li class="about-vision-item">
          <span class="about-vision-numeral">IV</span>
          <h3 class="about-vision-label"><em>Public leaders</em></h3>
          <p class="about-vision-body">Formed in character, limits, and locality.</p>
        </li>
      </ol>

      <p class="about-vision-coda">
        This is why we write and speak about church, culture, formation, family, theology, technology, and more. Through faithfulness to Christ in every square inch of life, we seek the renewal of the Church and culture in our lifetime.
      </p>
    </div>
